MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- transfer/variants.py: generate_variants() now creates HookBinding per variant
- transfer/validator.py: detect empty hook_bindings → policy_violation
- patch_planning_stage.py: fail-closed checks for empty hook_bindings and changes
- patch_application_stage.py: pass validation steps to finalize, handle not_run checks
- All stages 3.1-3.7 pass end-to-end on run_l3_bottle_001
